{"tid":1677820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一招KO建制、偽黃L","createTime":"2019-10-27T10:15:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T11:35:21.000Z","uid":333542,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"922e2ec715c28ebfd9b782a7b4e910ebb4c6363a","tid":1677820,"uid":333542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:15:10.000Z","msg":"<strong>忽發奇想</strong><br />\n話說區選已經殺到埋身，仲有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">28日</span></span></strong>就到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">11月24</span></span>，咁我地喺呢段時間有咩可以做到呢？<br />\n就係......<br />\n當我地每逢見到<span style=\"color: red;\">建制</span>、<span style=\"color: blue;\">偽黃</span>候選人擺街站，都問佢班PK以下呢set問題(包括但不限於此)，然後全程錄低再dum上網，ultimate goal係send到去班姨媽姑爹<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">藍到仆街嘅whatsapp group </span></span></strong>，目的係要佢地睇到自己支持嘅人係幾撚無腦<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">簡單版</span></strong></span><br />\n1.你對六四有咩睇法？你支持平反六四嗎？<br />\n2.你知唔知咩係五大訴求？(要佢分別讀出)，你支唔支持五大訴求？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>中級版</strong></span></span><br />\n3.你心目中嘅烏托邦係點？(等佢講完)，咁你覺得港府目前嘅行為(警暴etc.)能夠達致你口中嘅理想世界嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">高級版</span></strong></span><br />\n4.一時間諗唔撚到，自己諗。總之要拋書包，講多啲概念詞or歷史，再問佢點睇<br />\n<br />\n大家先唔好覺得我onL9，話班建制L都無撚腦，做乜同佢地講道理乜乜乜。請記住，佢答你啲垃撚圾嘅答案係唔緊要嘅，換句話講，我地就係要佢答垃撚圾答案，然後up上社交媒體廣傳，我地係要<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一傳十、十傳百</span></span>呢個效果，等佢俾人感覺學識低，就好似馬鞍山條中立撚咁，而家喺沙田出晒名。<br />\n<br />\nP牌仔第一次出po，寫得唔好屌輕力啲"},{"pid":"1b0330a3aa37b6c063c98b29a6937bda33f20aee","tid":1677820,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:15:23.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"228cad94e5e4fbf4dac7e1ca812387ffad520c0b","tid":1677820,"uid":212918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be01c1d389d254e19d7ee3b1362d33fbb952c8f8","tid":1677820,"uid":282798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:28:43.000Z","msg":"推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983cb671b3687e8d4bfd4453da2ad1e2a6f31095","tid":1677820,"uid":244240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T10:32:55.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0e7b73eab30b804105a7224c9130ff7f7c697d06","tid":1677820,"uid":180097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-27T11:35:21.000Z","msg":"你上面提到嘅問題好似唔會阻止藍絲唔投佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}